  title: Empathy
  conversationText: 'Lena: I studied for two weeks and still failed.

    Omar: That
    sounds really discouraging.

    Lena: Everyone else just gets it naturally.

    Omar:
    That doesn''t mean you''re not capable.

    Lena: I just needed to hear that,
    thanks.'
