  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::SocialScenarios.DialogueEntry
  id: 2
  title: Assertiveness
  conversationText: 'Diane: I signed you up to present tomorrow.

    Theo: I wasn''t
    prepared for that at all.

    Diane: You''re the best at explaining things.

    Theo:
    You still should have asked me first.

    Diane: I figured you wouldn''t mind.'
